548
00:29:58,290 --> 00:30:00,520
you also had a contract with Rui.

549
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:03,220
If you want to terminate the contract,

550
00:30:03,220 --> 00:30:04,950
then you must follow the terms.

551
00:30:07,700 --> 00:30:09,730
Since I've brought it up to you,

552
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:11,950
it means I'm prepared

553
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:14,090
to honour the terms of the agreement.

554
00:30:14,300 --> 00:30:15,440
Yuan Yuan!

555
00:30:16,150 --> 00:30:17,250
Don't worry.

556
00:30:17,940 --> 00:30:19,510
I'll pay the termination fee

557
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:21,730
of five million and not a cent less.

558
00:30:24,510 --> 00:30:25,890
Can you afford it?

559
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:27,790
That's not your problem.

560
00:30:30,030 --> 00:30:32,640
So please be understanding.

561
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:36,560
Thanks.

562
00:30:38,670 --> 00:30:39,770
Yuan Yuan!

563
00:30:59,140 --> 00:31:01,160
How did this happen?

564
00:31:04,060 --> 00:31:05,630
Why?

565
00:31:06,670 --> 00:31:08,970
Stop fidgeting. You're making me dizzy.

566
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:16,400
Duan Ran.

567
00:31:17,390 --> 00:31:18,680
It's all your fault.

568
00:31:19,630 --> 00:31:21,500
We've been over this.

569
00:31:21,580 --> 00:31:23,420
I told you it won't work.

570
00:31:23,510 --> 00:31:26,100
You gave her all the traffic,
all the protection,

571
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:27,860
and all of the company's resources.

572
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:29,550
You think that was going to work?

573
00:31:29,550 --> 00:31:31,220
You didn't listen. Now look what happened.

574
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:33,620
I didn't know she'd
turn out this way, did I?

575
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:35,180
I did nothing wrong.

576
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:37,800
What? It was totally your fault.

577
00:31:40,740 --> 00:31:42,090
If it's not your fault,

578
00:31:42,310 --> 00:31:44,250
then tell me, what should we do?

579
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:47,040
Can we even negotiate?

580
00:31:48,030 --> 00:31:50,030
Since Yuan Yuan took it upon herself

581
00:31:50,090 --> 00:31:53,210
to pay you five million to terminate
the contract,

582
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:55,700
it means she's not interested
in negotiating.

583
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:57,790
She was just informing you.

584
00:31:59,390 --> 00:32:01,320
Five million yuan.

585
00:32:02,150 --> 00:32:04,250
Can she fork out the cash?

586
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:07,440
I know full well how much she makes.

587
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:08,870
Her family isn't rich,

588
00:32:08,870 --> 00:32:09,820
and she has

589
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:11,250
many mouths to feed.

590
00:32:11,420 --> 00:32:12,850
She can't pay the amount.

591
00:32:13,750 --> 00:32:15,480
Since she had the gall to say it,

592
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:18,090
she must have her ways, right?

593
00:32:18,180 --> 00:32:19,910
We signed that contract

594
00:32:20,060 --> 00:32:22,250
as an assurance to both of us.

595
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:23,890
Having that assurance

596
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:25,460
gave me the confidence

597
00:32:25,550 --> 00:32:27,210
to put all our best resources,

598
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:28,720
all our money on her.

599
00:32:28,910 --> 00:32:30,630
Now that the assurance is gone,

600
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:32,970
we ought to get back our money.

601
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:38,090
Actually, this isn't about the money.

602
00:32:40,150 --> 00:32:42,560
Do you know what I feel
the most hurt about?

603
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:44,660
It's her strong,

604
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:47,010
Aries-like streak of individualism.

605
00:32:47,790 --> 00:32:49,890
She didn't even let me have a say

606
00:32:50,500 --> 00:32:53,500
before she decided to shell out
the five million yuan.

607
00:32:53,510 --> 00:32:55,090
What am I to her?

608
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:57,040
I feel so manipulated.

609
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:04,010
You...

610
00:33:12,790 --> 00:33:15,130
Cancers like you are no slouch either.

611
00:33:17,990 --> 00:33:20,160
Tough and fierce on the outside,

612
00:33:20,300 --> 00:33:22,640
soft and fuzzy on the inside.

613
00:33:23,820 --> 00:33:24,920
Isn't that right?

614
00:33:25,670 --> 00:33:26,770
Right?

615
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,680
Give me a break.

616
00:33:34,910 --> 00:33:37,050
Can't you pick a better time
to flatter me?

617
00:33:37,050 --> 00:33:39,250
You're obviously trying to console me.

618
00:33:43,120 --> 00:33:44,820
Then tell me,

619
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:47,160
what am I going to do?

620
00:33:50,810 --> 00:33:51,910
Two things.

621
00:33:52,340 --> 00:33:53,440
First,

622
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:56,890
Yuan Yuan's departure

623
00:33:57,300 --> 00:33:58,680
is a fact.

624
00:33:59,060 --> 00:34:00,150
You can't change it.

625
00:34:00,150 --> 00:34:01,850
So after she leaves,

626
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:04,730
you should fill up that void
as soon as possible.

627
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:08,380
Everything from the broadcaster
to the supply chain

628
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:09,780
should be restructured.

629
00:34:10,989 --> 00:34:12,400
That's a lot to handle.

630
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:14,420
The die is cast.

631
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:16,840
We have to move on
no matter how difficult.

632
00:34:17,219 --> 00:34:18,320
What's second?

633
00:34:18,790 --> 00:34:22,570
If Yuan Yuan wants
to pay you five million yuan,

634
00:34:23,929 --> 00:34:26,330
just take it.

635
00:34:28,699 --> 00:34:30,570
That's true, but...

636
00:34:33,110 --> 00:34:34,920
Ms Qian, Mr Duan.

637
00:34:36,310 --> 00:34:38,460
Ms Qian, is this a good time?

638
00:34:38,550 --> 00:34:39,840
No, it's not.

639
00:34:42,030 --> 00:34:43,570
Well, of course it is.

640
00:34:44,790 --> 00:34:45,889
Go.

641
00:34:49,620 --> 00:34:51,330
Be strong. Come on.

642
00:34:54,409 --> 00:34:55,600
I'm off, then.

643
00:34:56,310 --> 00:34:58,970
The company comes first. Save the company.

644
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:20,900
Ms Qian, I know you
must be furious at Yuan Yuan.

645
00:35:20,990 --> 00:35:22,830
But it's an opportunity of a lifetime.

646
00:35:22,830 --> 00:35:23,860
This is the big break

647
00:35:23,860 --> 00:35:25,180
Yuan Yuan has been waiting for.

648
00:35:25,180 --> 00:35:26,510
She's got her big break.

649
00:35:26,650 --> 00:35:28,550
But does that mean she can abandon us?

650
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:29,650
It's not like that.

651
00:35:29,940 --> 00:35:31,500
If Yuan Yuan had a better choice,

652
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:32,960
she wouldn't have done so.

653
00:35:34,270 --> 00:35:38,360
Ms Qian, I apologise to you
on Yuan Yuan's behalf.

654
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:40,400
I'm really sorry.

655
00:35:42,940 --> 00:35:44,730
That's enough, Zhang Bin.

656
00:35:46,070 --> 00:35:48,660
I understand why Yuan Yuan
made this decision.

657
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:50,860
But she tried to sever ties with me
out of the blue,

658
00:35:50,860 --> 00:35:52,660
even at the cost of five million.

659
00:35:52,700 --> 00:35:55,700
Does she have the money?
Does she respect my feelings?

660
00:35:55,940 --> 00:35:58,010
Ms Qian, I came here

661
00:35:58,130 --> 00:35:59,840
just to talk about that.

662
00:36:01,100 --> 00:36:03,360
I'm sure you know Yuan Yuan's character.

663
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:06,160
She's on the reckless side.

664
00:36:06,900 --> 00:36:08,380
I know she wants out,

665
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:09,420
but I didn't know

666
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:10,700
she'd do it by the book

667
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:12,300
and pay the termination fee.

668
00:36:13,110 --> 00:36:14,590
When she came out of your office,

669
00:36:14,590 --> 00:36:17,810
she told me to put her car and her house
up for sale online.

670
00:36:21,990 --> 00:36:23,750
She's selling her car and her house?

671
00:36:23,750 --> 00:36:24,850
Yes.

672
00:36:25,620 --> 00:36:29,330
You know her family's situation,
don't you?

673
00:36:29,820 --> 00:36:31,180
The only assets she has

674
00:36:31,270 --> 00:36:33,490
are her house in Xiamen and her car.

675
00:36:35,700 --> 00:36:37,440
If she sells them off,

676
00:36:37,850 --> 00:36:39,390
what would become of her?

677
00:36:44,220 --> 00:36:45,400
Ms Qian,

678
00:36:46,210 --> 00:36:48,440
I know in everyone's eyes,

679
00:36:48,900 --> 00:36:50,810
I'm just a small fry.

680
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,880
But I just want to take this chance

681
00:36:53,460 --> 00:36:55,570
to tell you how I feel.

682
00:37:06,020 --> 00:37:07,160
Sit down.

683
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:17,050
The truth is, I'm a fan of Yuan Yuan's.

684
00:37:22,350 --> 00:37:24,160
Everybody knows that.

685
00:37:24,940 --> 00:37:26,880
At first, I wasn't a fan of hers

686
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:28,630
but of some other starlet's.

687
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:30,140
So I got together

688
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:33,050
with a few other fans and went to
the set to see her.

689
00:37:35,110 --> 00:37:36,840
But upon interacting with her,

690
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:41,160
I realised my idol was nothing like
her celebrity persona.

691
00:37:41,660 --> 00:37:43,080
I was disappointed.

692
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:47,010
I sat under a tree,
leaning against its trunk.

693
00:37:47,610 --> 00:37:49,860
Then I heard someone speaking
to me from above,

694
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:52,210
asking if I could get her a packed lunch.

695
00:37:54,460 --> 00:37:55,570
Yuan Yuan?

696
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:58,070
That was the first time I saw Yuan Yuan.

697
00:37:58,110 --> 00:38:00,370
She was in her wired costume,

698
00:38:00,460 --> 00:38:02,010
hanging on the tree.

699
00:38:02,310 --> 00:38:03,970
The crew had gone out to lunch.

700
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:06,430
I didn't want to mess up her costume,

701
00:38:06,590 --> 00:38:08,360
so I...

702
00:38:08,900 --> 00:38:10,680
I fetched her a packed lunch.

703
00:38:13,180 --> 00:38:14,280
I get it.

704
00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:16,030
You took a shine to Yuan Yuan

705
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:17,490
from that moment on.

706
00:38:18,350 --> 00:38:19,640
Not so soon.

707
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:22,220
So I took the packed lunch
in one hand

708
00:38:22,310 --> 00:38:23,950
and fed her with the other.

709
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:25,630
Her hands were tied, you see.

710
00:38:26,220 --> 00:38:27,380
Since that incident,

711
00:38:27,380 --> 00:38:29,160
I began to notice her.

712
00:38:29,420 --> 00:38:32,680
I discovered that she was an extremely
dedicated actress.

713
00:38:32,790 --> 00:38:33,890
Since then,

714
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:37,680
I decided to become Qi Yuan Yuan's
number one fan.

715
00:38:39,590 --> 00:38:40,690
Zhang Bin,

716
00:38:43,990 --> 00:38:46,210
I hear you used to be a top executive

717
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:47,740
at an internet company.

718
00:38:47,830 --> 00:38:50,360
I worked 12 hours a day, six days a week.

719
00:38:51,350 --> 00:38:52,760
After meeting Yuan Yuan,

720
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:54,900
I felt showbiz was too tough for her,

721
00:38:55,380 --> 00:38:57,440
so I suggested she go into streaming.

722
00:38:58,660 --> 00:39:01,810
Seeing her become the head broadcaster

723
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:04,210
makes me rather proud.

724
00:39:09,420 --> 00:39:10,810
Do you know why

725
00:39:11,030 --> 00:39:12,590
we were so upset when she tried

726
00:39:12,590 --> 00:39:14,120
to end her contract with us?

727
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:17,120
Because she's the pride of our company.

728
00:39:20,070 --> 00:39:23,130
I know it's not easy for you and Mr Duan
to start a business.

729
00:39:23,130 --> 00:39:26,130
But it's no easier for Yuan Yuan
to get this far either.

730
00:39:27,380 --> 00:39:28,920
So I beg you,

731
00:39:29,940 --> 00:39:33,120
seeing as we are all still young,

732
00:39:33,370 --> 00:39:36,290
seeing as we have a long road ahead of us,

733
00:39:37,530 --> 00:39:39,470
can you please go easy on her

734
00:39:39,700 --> 00:39:40,920
and let her off?

735
00:39:43,220 --> 00:39:46,220
Don't make her sell her house and her car.

736
00:39:46,730 --> 00:39:48,540
Let her accumulate some wealth.

737
00:39:49,570 --> 00:39:52,310
In the future,
if she runs into any trouble,

738
00:39:52,850 --> 00:39:56,790
please show her some
kindness and generosity.

739
00:40:05,090 --> 00:40:06,190
What are you doing?

740
00:40:30,770 --> 00:40:33,740
[Time, It's time to show]

741
00:40:35,650 --> 00:40:36,900
There's just one issue

742
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:38,920
about the movie.

743
00:40:39,170 --> 00:40:42,600
He's going to play
a murderer in "The Suspect".

744
00:40:43,380 --> 00:40:47,050
Madam, can you please
stop harping on that?

745
00:40:47,140 --> 00:40:48,240
Alright?

746
00:40:48,380 --> 00:40:49,480
So, Ms Ouyang,

747
00:40:49,700 --> 00:40:51,330
after all that drivel,

748
00:40:51,420 --> 00:40:53,000
just say it plainly.

749
00:40:53,090 --> 00:40:56,120
Just tell me I'm short-sighted.

750
00:40:56,210 --> 00:40:58,430
Madam, that's not what I mean.

751
00:40:59,050 --> 00:41:00,400
If you think...

752
00:41:00,490 --> 00:41:01,440
That's enough.

753
00:41:01,530 --> 00:41:03,310
Let's not argue anymore.

754
00:41:03,420 --> 00:41:05,620
Look at you, you've been working so hard

755
00:41:05,690 --> 00:41:07,140
with barely any time to rest.

756
00:41:07,140 --> 00:41:09,600
You should kick back, take it easy.

757
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:11,190
Have you had dinner?

758
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:13,720
I'll get you a bowl
of Guilin rice noodles.

759
00:41:13,810 --> 00:41:15,230
No need to, Madam.

760
00:41:15,420 --> 00:41:16,590
Seriously.

761
00:41:50,940 --> 00:41:52,040
Have some water.

762
00:42:02,330 --> 00:42:04,080
Don't worry. Keep training.

763
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:08,330
Isn't Xiao Yu in "The Suspect"

764
00:42:08,410 --> 00:42:10,070
supposed to be a beefcake?

765
00:42:14,290 --> 00:42:15,390
I need to get this.

766
00:42:15,620 --> 00:42:16,720
Sure.

767
00:42:19,850 --> 00:42:21,070
Hello, Duan Ran.

768
00:42:21,810 --> 00:42:23,210
I've been so busy lately.

769
00:42:23,250 --> 00:42:25,050
I wanted to get in touch with you.

770
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:28,150
I'm guessing you want to see me?

771
00:42:29,040 --> 00:42:31,020
Guess what it's about?

772
00:42:31,500 --> 00:42:33,110
About work stuff, I guess.

773
00:42:33,370 --> 00:42:34,360
I heard.

774
00:42:34,450 --> 00:42:36,560
Your big time broadcaster Yuan Yuan

775
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:39,190
just got a movie deal and wants to split.

776
00:42:39,530 --> 00:42:43,180
It must cost your company
plenty of viewership.

777
00:42:43,450 --> 00:42:45,560
But Yang Yang's been busy, too.

778
00:42:45,650 --> 00:42:46,960
He's not available.

779
00:42:47,170 --> 00:42:48,550
I'm not asking for him.

780
00:42:50,370 --> 00:42:51,830
Then who?

781
00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:54,490
Can you set me up with someone

782
00:42:54,580 --> 00:42:56,250
who has a big following?

783
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:58,560
Some kind of internet celebrity.

784
00:42:59,450 --> 00:43:00,610
[Sure, I'll think about it.]

785
00:43:00,610 --> 00:43:01,790
[I have to check]

786
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:02,930
[their schedules first.]

787
00:43:02,930 --> 00:43:04,450
[If I find anyone suitable]

788
00:43:04,450 --> 00:43:05,600
[and available,]

789
00:43:05,690 --> 00:43:06,930
[I'll fix you up.]

790
00:43:07,020 --> 00:43:09,450
Thanks. Just what I'd expect
from a top notch agent.

791
00:43:09,450 --> 00:43:10,920
One phone call is all it takes.

792
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:12,180
I'll wait for the news.

793
00:43:12,370 --> 00:43:14,100
[Sure. I'll talk to you again.]

794
00:43:14,530 --> 00:43:15,630
[Bye-bye.]

795
00:43:17,850 --> 00:43:18,950
What is it?
